{"tid":2426398,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"人民日報：「吳孟達一輩子配角，但論愛国是主角」","createTime":"2021-02-28T05:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T07:55:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"57b7f0d5d5a5315e481c80e09b046e58fc05ae14","tid":2426398,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:31:37.000Z","msg":"《人民日報》今日（28日）刊文悼念，表示吳對祖國的熱愛，代表了香港人的主流價值觀，卻有宵小之徒在社交媒體上無恥地惡語相向，並直言吳孟達演了一輩子配角，但論愛國卻一直是主角。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》指，吳孟達病逝令香港和內地的網民陷入悲痛之中。他塑造了無數經典角色，為觀眾帶來歡樂和思考，陪伴了幾代人的青春。即使演了一輩子配角，但吳對角色不曾敷衍，令人看到一位戲骨的敬業精神，也感受到他對藝術追求。<br />\n<br />\n文章稱，吳孟達生前留下的最後一條微博寫有「我是中國人」，令無數網民集體致敬。而透過短短5個字，更讓人讀懂他對國家樸素而自然的愛。觀眾緬懷和尊重吳，不僅因為他演技精湛，更重要的是他有一顆乾淨、滾燙的愛國之心，正如有網民所稱：「藝術無國界，藝術家有祖國」。<br />\n<br />\n文章又指，吳孟達最純粹的愛國情感，卻戳中香港部分宵小之徒的痛處，在社交媒體上向他潑髒水、貼標籤，無所不用其極。而此番操弄，更再次暴露出宵小之徒逢中必反到了缺乏人性、沒有底線的地步，對愛國者的仇視到了喪心病狂的地步。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，宵小之徒愈是攻擊愛國者，就愈反襯出吳孟達心怀大義；愈是惱羞成怒，愈說明吳的人格高大。事實上，在香港像吳一樣愛國的人才是大多數，他們或許不是亮眼明星，或許從未有過轟轟烈烈的舉動，但在大是大非前絕不糊塗。<br />\n<br />\n文章最後指，在香港，吳孟達和熱愛國家的人永遠都是主角，而流淌在血液中的情感，能夠讓他們與反中亂港分子劃清界限，攜手背靠祖國、守護香港、建設家園。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01 .com/即時中國/592862</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8038156cae4b9e872d3e21eaa63498c675896095","tid":2426398,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":16,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"&rdquo;我真係好撚鍾意香港&rdquo;既連登仔<br />\n對香港輝煌時代，帶俾香港人各種集體回憶<br />\n有份創造香港流行文化既個班人毫無珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至有好多都唔係衝出黎屌佢地<br />\n只係政見同佢地唔一樣就下下要打要殺<br />\n慶祝人死，只可以話我好好彩呢班廢柴成唔到事<br />\n俾佢地管既香港十成十仲恐撚怖過共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337b4f00b23ed04136100de55650f595a646f3bb","tid":2426398,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"老納"},{"pid":"2e4dbf2e2b135681bc5633655b3943b1db99cb62","tid":2426398,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvpDswD.jpg&amp;h=931b8a63&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"fdd7cf24884d3f31cd63fa5368ce27ccb9fc484b","tid":2426398,"uid":301529,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"#2咁快有隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d9cad50a711229c9b2c695852362b308b8b01e","tid":2426398,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdd7cf24884d3f31cd63fa5368ce27ccb9fc484b","tid":2426398,"uid":301529,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"#2咁快有隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b364ab4d4ce04b4c2268f1eadf07b3a3aa3b9d1","tid":2426398,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass